The paper discusses a technique for approximate inference tasks in AI and machine learning, which suggests that it belongs to the cs.AI sub-category. The paper also proposes a sequential approach to adding new clusters of nodes and their interactions, which involves computational complexity and efficient measures, indicating that it could also belong to the cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT, and cs.SI sub-categories.
